  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK552">
<l>vēloṭu niṉṟā ṉiṭuveṉ ṟatupōluṅ </l>
<l>kōloṭu niṉṟā ṉiravu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The request (for money) of him who holds the sceptre is like the word of a highway robber who stands with a weapon in hand and says "give up your wealth".</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
